    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n    <strong>School</strong>&nbsp;transmutation;\n    <strong>Level</strong>&nbsp;alchemist 2, magus 3, sorcerer/wizard 3, witch 3;\n    \n    \n    \n    \n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Casting Time</strong>&nbsp;1 standard action<br>\n    <strong>Components</strong>&nbsp;V, S, M (a cocoon tied with string)<br>\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Range</strong>&nbsp;personal<br>\n    \n    <strong>Targets</strong>&nbsp;you<br>\n    \n    <strong>Duration</strong>&nbsp;1 minute/level<br>\n    \n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  <p>For the duration of this spell, your vital organs writhe, shift, and move about, making it difficult to strike you in a vulnerable area. While this spell is in effect, critical hits and sneak attacks against you have a 25% chance of failing to inflict any additional damage-though you still take the normal damage from the attack. At 7th level, the chance to ignore additional damage increases to 50%, while at 13th level the chance increases to 75%.</p>\n</div>\n",
